data.value: mClarkAssignment1 A Form Class implementing the following controls and event procedures: 1. A label at the top of the form that displays the name of your movie (make up a name) 2. A label to display the appropriate name (i.e., actor’s, actress’ or director’s) 3. Four buttons labeled “Lead Actor”, “Lead Actress”, “Director” and “Exit”. 4. The click event procedure for the first three buttons should instantiate a Movie object, call the appropriate method and display the result in a label (see 2 above) 5. The click event for the Exit button should close the form 6. A label at the bottom of the form that displays your name as the developer
